💼 Personal Portfolio Website
A fully responsive Personal Portfolio Website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript as part of the CodSoft Virtual Internship. This project showcases web development skills by creating a professional portfolio that highlights personal information, skills, projects, and contact details.

📌 Features
✔️ Responsive and modern UI/UX
✔️ Home, About, Skills, Projects, and Contact sections
✔️ Smooth scrolling and interactive animations
✔️ Mobile-friendly design
✔️ Social media and contact form integration
✔️ Dynamic elements using JavaScript

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5 - Structuring the website
CSS3 - Styling and layout (Flexbox, Grid, Animations)
JavaScript - Interactivity and smooth scrolling
Google Fonts & FontAwesome (for typography and icons)
EmailJS (if used for the contact form)
